Once per turn, during either player's turn: You can discard 1 "Ninja" monster, then activate 1 of these effects;
<br><b>-</b> This turn, "Ninja" monsters and "Ninjitsu Art" cards you control cannot be destroyed by battle or card effects.
<br><b>-</b> 1 "Ninja" monster you control gains 1000 ATK until the end of this turn.
